"Depending on your use, your phone may contain confidential information (photos, passwords, card numbers or bank accounts, etc.).
The loss of this information may occur in the following cases: n - loss or theft of the phone - installation of malicious or simply poorly programmed applications
In order to avoid any inconvenience, SFR recommends that you follow the following recommendations: - activate password protection of the phone - activate automatic locking after a few minutes of inactivity - check the reputation of applications and their publisher before installing them - check the authorization requests issued by an application during its installation or of its use. If in doubt, deny permission. - before giving your phone for recycling, remember to destroy all your data and reset the operating system"
